l will just write about Phyllis.
好，那我就来写菲莉丝

239
00:14:55,194 --> 00:14:58,527
-''Phyllis is sitting in the chair. ''
-l see what you're doing.
菲莉丝坐在椅子上。我知道你想干嘛

240
00:14:58,964 --> 00:15:01,398
''Phyllis sees what l'm doing. ''
菲莉丝知道我想干嘛

241
