l have tasted my own medicine
and it is bitter!
哇，我终于自食恶 果了

242
00:15:13,045 --> 00:15:14,205
Morning!


243
00:15:14,813 --> 00:15:17,281
How's my favorite genius
and his robot?
我最欣赏的天才 和我的机器人兄弟好吗？

244
00:15:17,516 --> 00:15:19,609
-Don't touch him!
-Okay.
别碰他

245
00:15:21,620 --> 00:15:25,818
Level with me. l keep hearing
rumors that l might get fired.
韦恩，你老实说。 我一直听说我会被换掉

246
00:15:26,158 --> 00:15:29,150
They even have actors reading
for my part.
他们还找人来试我这个角色

247
00:15:29,628 --> 00:15:32,096
Come on. You gotta give me
a second chance.
拜托啦，再给我一次机会

248
00:15:32,331 --> 00:15:33,958
l love this little guy.
我爱死这个小家伙…

249
00:15:36,402 --> 00:15:38,996
That's why you didn't want me
to touch him, right?
难怪你不让我碰他，拿去吧

250
00:15:42,441 --> 00:15:44,966
l can't believe it. God!
白痴，真是的

251
00:15:46,345 --> 00:15:48,836
Hey, how are you doing?
你好吗？

252
00:15:53,686 --> 00:15:57,019
So it seemed that my prom date
had stood me up.
看样子我是被放鸽子了

253
