谢谢，你也是

305
00:19:14,786 --> 00:19:17,914
l told you l should
not wear this color.
我就说我不该穿这个颜色

306
00:19:20,692 --> 00:19:26,187
''Monica... Marsha and Chester are
planning on seeing a movie Sunday.
摩…摩莎和钱特 打算星期天晚上去看电影

307
00:19:27,032 --> 00:19:31,401
''Marsha thinks they're meeting at
6:00. Chester thinks it's 7:00.''
摩莎觉得应该约6点 钱特觉得电影是7点

308
00:19:32,171 --> 00:19:35,163
-You knew we were gonna miss the movie?
-Right.
你知道我们会赶不上电影？ 没错

309
00:19:35,641 --> 00:19:40,078
lnstead of telling us, you decided
to write it in your stupid book?
而你只把它写下来 不告诉我们？

310
00:19:40,279 --> 00:19:42,770
''Marsha and Chester
are mad at Phyllis. ''
摩莎和钱特很气菲莉丝

311
00:19:48,554 --> 00:19:50,613
l can't believe
l'm gonna lose this job.
