ls there anything l can do?
真可惜，我能帮什么忙吗？

313
00:19:53,959 --> 00:19:58,055
Help me get this mini-fridge
past the security guard.
能，帮我把那个小冰箱搬走

314
00:20:02,935 --> 00:20:04,994
Joey, l want to talk to you.
